summary: Ehhy oh! My first legit Commission sheet hopefully in full quality for you all! Please Re-Blog and get the word out. I’m a...
caption:
Ehhy oh! My first legit Commission sheet hopefully in full quality for you all!

Please Re-Blog and get the word out. I’m a desperate 19 year old trying to get a drivers license 

I have a Ko-Fi too! Any Questions Message me here, For commissions hit up my email under the “Keep Reading”

Please Note: My commissions are not a “first come first serve basis”! I will view commissions that resonate with me and my art style In order to give an image of high dedication and quality! Your image may be re-imagined in this process. (Of course, I will not do major changes i.e Oc hair is blue and I make it green)

Rules!

____________

  • PAYMENT IS UPFRONT! PLEASE DO NOT SEND ME MONEY WITHOUT ME MESSAGING YOU FIRST!
  • Commissions will only be accepted through Email. (I’m a cluttered mess and Tumblr is too with it’s notifications.)
  • No Backgrounds (Most images come with a simple color and/or texture. Atmospherics come with a blurred environmental background free!)
  • Extra Characters are an Extra 10 bucks (Sorry I need to make a livin’)
  • I need a visual reference! Even a collage of random images that describe your character can do! Existing art is also super helpful! If you have a description keep it simple and to the point.
  • Furthermore: Send me the most recently updated references of your commission. I beg not to send constant revisions whilst I’m working on a commission.
  • I will reply to you in the next 24 hours, If you don not respond, I unfortunately have to throw your commission away (That does not mean you can never get one from me ever again, just try again lol

___________

Commissions take about 4 to 5 weeks to complete! Depending on which commission you choose this can be much shorter or longer!

____________

Will Draw: 

Humans, Original Characters, Monsters, Creatures, Characters from Video games / T.V Shows / Movies ect. Gore, Horror. Some Animals.

_____________

WILL NOT DRAW:

F/ets)h -Art, Anime, Robots, Furries, Backgrounds (I will make exceptions to these just message me abt if curious)

_____________

Welp! Since you made it this far! Hit me up at

~Wakajack2.0@gmail.com~ Once again I also have a Ko-Fi!
